{"tid":481062,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(歐洲上雪山)鐵力士山Titlis定楚格峰Zugspitze好","createTime":"2017-11-26T18:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T15:40:49.000Z","uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f52710bbd41373857387f35dedaabe9bdff8e042","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:40:02.000Z","msg":"人在德國，見兩座山差唔多高，但價錢差好遠，<br />\nTitlis會由Lucerne出發，計埋交通住宿都貴過Zugspitze 30幾歐，<br />\n但之前去zurich atm出問題禁多左瑞士法郎，<br />\n而家仲有好多淨，唱返歐羅要蝕幾歐所以先猶豫去唔去Titlis好，<br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61ce5459182f876b193ebd171fdbb0a785d3a3d","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T22:37:01.000Z","msg":"睇過去雪山個2日都多雲,好頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9435691553013d85ab9941091c6c6eeeef953f","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b3f83c3922fb02c23390af36207a28cb383c14","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ed8d13c343a222455ae35fdf0b932c2ec816f6","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828e122d94512ebfa7ca868defbf43240c094710","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddfd039882a59ac0fa44658729e7e45248eec69","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ce40b4b9730fbf347d28cc6e151ba10399af02","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:42:58.000Z","msg":"8連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0741e09afffe26b1ec920ef415594cb7a6e34c16","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T19:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c561096fdfcd7b4574c1a83b9bf144761d9e4c","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T22:00:23.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f2adeaff4849ebb2fb9de263f4c9dd46c09efb","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46460a73881cee616fc1a8d467c2674251bbfa00","tid":481062,"uid":82718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"未去過Titlis 去楚格峰可以順便去埋Mittenwald 幾有特色嘅小鎮<br />\nbetween 兩個地方都隔好遠"},{"pid":"f44082532b5c8e737925bf7be692190eb29d3a4f","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b99318f830378c4e5a56680f150104b35fb3124","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未去過Titlis 去楚格峰可以順便去埋Mittenwald 幾有特色嘅小鎮<br />\nbetween 兩個地方都隔好遠</blockquote><br />\n所以要揀一個去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇介紹mittenwald幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569d538e91cef9ba834182f5706bbada28e35821","tid":481062,"uid":122939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"二個都去過，會揀Zugspitz, Titlus好多團隊去。"},{"pid":"004b533fda757d77a2a9ebf564c97bfe98493fa2","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二個都去過，會揀Zugspitz, Titlus好多團隊去。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇隔離post遊記話Titlis有好多印度同強國人"},{"pid":"39cb658720c55293facca4e6eba2df55e7db7402","tid":481062,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>二個都去過，會揀Zugspitz, Titlus好多團隊去。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇隔離post遊記話Titlis有好多印度同強國人</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真呀，見好多印度朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc0e286c686f065b204794d617e77048b6b153a","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>二個都去過，會揀Zugspitz, Titlus好多團隊去。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇隔離post遊記話Titlis有好多印度同強國人</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真呀，見好多印度朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我早去會唔會少啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋係咪兩個景感覺都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c73d2ccec5e2a1aefa89c0e353f2c6f52b705a0","tid":481062,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"Titlis係for 印度和強國 你都要照上冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9aecc3efdc29a88484ea694f043e42af697056","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Titlis係for 印度和強國 你都要照上冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉啲瑞士法郎要點洗咗佢"},{"pid":"182c54174f1219cc156cdd00b1a78dc66326f5de","tid":481062,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Titlis係for 印度和強國 你都要照上冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉啲瑞士法郎要點洗咗佢</blockquote><br />\n你都講真係要唱返瑞士法朗都係差幾歐<br />\n最重要去到想去既地方<br />\n<br />\n去過楚格峰<br />\n又好似唔太覺太多旅行團"},{"pid":"c2305fb3459e2f6e89386ba7248edaaab8714b0c","tid":481062,"uid":10165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Titlis係for 印度和強國 你都要照上冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉啲瑞士法郎要點洗咗佢</blockquote><br />\n你都講真係要唱返瑞士法朗都係差幾歐<br />\n最重要去到想去既地方<br />\n<br />\n去過楚格峰<br />\n又好似唔太覺太多旅行團</blockquote><br />\n楚格峰多本地人滑雪 食野都唔多貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c3ced367f659b6fd7cdece0a304acadd65bff9","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Titlis係for 印度和強國 你都要照上冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉啲瑞士法郎要點洗咗佢</blockquote><br />\n你都講真係要唱返瑞士法朗都係差幾歐<br />\n最重要去到想去既地方<br />\n<br />\n去過楚格峰<br />\n又好似唔太覺太多旅行團</blockquote><br />\n楚格峰多本地人滑雪 食野都唔多貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純粹想去一次雪山，兩邊搭車又方便，<br />\n好頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0930a685b6a0c869d184457a5f82c945109a9ff8","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207b4c0c98b7cafa20319a5f84b07e7041d6755b","tid":481062,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}